Doodle Jump is an addictive and entertaining game available as a Chrome Extension. It can also be played for free on the website monkeymart.org. In this game, players control a cute character called Doodler, whose goal is to jump as high as possible on a series of platforms without falling. The platforms are constantly moving and can include obstacles and enemies that must be avoided. Players can use springs and jetpacks to aid their ascent and collect power-ups for extra boosts. With simple controls and vibrant graphics, "Doodle Jump" offers endless fun and challenges as players strive to reach new heights and set high scores. Whether you're looking for a quick gaming session or a way to pass the time, "Doodle Jump" is a fantastic choice.
